Mutating and Arranging

gsw <- filter(dat, team == "GSW")
gsw <- select(gsw, player, height, weight)
gsw <- slice(gsw, c(4, 8, 10, 14, 15))
gsw
## # A tibble: 5 x 3
##           player height weight
